

Data Source
The source data is taken from this website:
http://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/Human+Activity+Recognition+Using+Smartphones

The link to the zip folder containing data set:
https://d396qusza40orc.cloudfront.net/getdata%2Fprojectfiles%2FUCI%20HAR%20Dataset.zip

The dataset includes 28 files containing details of the results of an experiment carried out on 30 individuals.  The dataset was split in two with 70% selected for the training set and 30% for the test set.  A full description can be found on the website above.

The following 6 files relating to the training/test sets were extracted:  
.	test/subject_test.txt
.	test/X_test.txt
.	test/y_test.txt
.	train/subject_train.txt
.	train/X_train.txt
.	train/y_train.txt

The files were combined to create a single dataset.

Description

Characteristics: Multivariate, Time series

Name	       Number of Rows	   Number of Columns
FinalData3	    10,299	              68

Variable Description

Variable	                Description	                                  R Data Type
subject	          Unique subject identifier	                                Integer (1.30)
activity	        Activities performed by subjects in experiment	    Factor (6 levels)
Columns 3:68	    Mean and standard deviations of various             Numeric
                  measurements relating to the experiment
		

Details of the transformations performed on the original data sets to generate the dataset "FinalData3" are set out in the markdown document Getting.Cleaning_Data_Project.Rmd
